<p>-Welcome to the Village at Main Street. We are professionally managed and have a friendly and knowledgeable staff from the leasing office to the maintenance technicians.
<p>When convenience and location mean everything, The Village at Main Street has just what you'll need to make yourself feel right at home! This Community was designed and built to offer you a neighborhood feel. Featuring one, two, three-bedroom apartments, and townhome options with well-designed open rooms, expansive windows, and a private patio or balcony.<br><br>Village at Main Street has unprecedented amenities to choose from like enjoying a good game of billiards, catching a movie in the theater room, working out in a state of the art three-story center called Edge Fitness that is FREE to all of our residents, or relaxing at our junior Olympic pool, we've got a little bit of everything for everybody! <br><br>Located in the heart of Wilsonville, Village at Main Street is close enough to enjoy the city of life of downtown Portland to the North and the calmness of Salem to the South. For those who want to venture out on foot - food, drink, shopping and much more are all within just walking distance! <br><br>If that wasn't enough, Wilsonville's landscaped village streets offer running and walking trails at the Memorial Park Murase Plaza, Town Center Park, and Graham Oaks Nature Park Trailhead. The scenic Willamette River, three 18-hole public and private golf courses, and the Willamette public library are just a stone's throw away. Find it all at The Village at Main!<br><br> Click to take a tour of our gym! https://youtu.be/TOE-oNRhwq4<br>Visit our website for more details and availability http://www.villageatmain.com/
